title: Nothing Is Real (feat. Ron Bennington, Andy Fiori & Shane Gillis)
description: Dan and Jay discuss crazy ex girlfriends and bad break ups. Andy Fiori & Dan's old drinking/hangover stories. Ron Bennington joins the show and talks about his old co-host Fez coming out on air.
